      <p class="faq-updated">
        <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>
        {% endraw %}{% set _iso = page.inputPath | gitDateISO %}{% if _iso %}<time datetime="{{ _iso }}">Last updated {{ _iso | humanDate("en") }}</time>{% else %}<span>Recently updated</span>{% endif %}{% raw %}
      </p>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <nav class="faq-rail" aria-label="FAQ categories">
          <p class="faq-rail-h">Categories</p>
          <button class="faq-cat is-active" data-target="faq-g1"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 3v18"/><path d="M5 4h13l-3 4 3 4H5z"/></svg><span class="faq-cat-n">Getting started</span><span class="faq-cat-c">4</span></button>
          <button class="faq-cat" data-target="faq-g2"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/></svg><span class="faq-cat-n">The competition</span><span class="faq-cat-c">6</span></button>
          <button class="faq-cat" data-target="faq-g3"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="16" height="16" x="4" y="4" rx="2"/><rect width="6" height="6" x="9" y="9" rx="1"/><path d="M9 2v2"/><path d="M15 2v2"/><path d="M9 20v2"/><path d="M15 20v2"/><path d="M2 9h2"/><path d="M2 15h2"/><path d="M20 9h2"/><path d="M20 15h2"/></svg><span class="faq-cat-n">Compute</span><span class="faq-cat-c">2</span></button>
          <button class="faq-cat" data-target="faq-g4"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526"/></svg><span class="faq-cat-n">AMD award</span><span class="faq-cat-c">1</span></button>
          <button class="faq-cat" data-target="faq-g5"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z"/></svg><span class="faq-cat-n">Stay connected</span><span class="faq-cat-c">1</span></button>
        </nav>

        <div class="faq-cards">
          <section class="faq-card" id="faq-g1">
            <div class="faq-card-h"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 3v18"/><path d="M5 4h13l-3 4 3 4H5z"/></svg><h2>Getting started</h2><span class="faq-card-c">4 questions</span></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">How do I register?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Register a team of 1–6 on the <a href="register.html">registration page</a>. Member 1 is the point of contact and receives all team email.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">Is there an entry fee?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>No — participation is free.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">Can I compete solo, or do I form my own team?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Teams are 1–6 people; solo is allowed, and you form your own team. Looking for teammates? Use our <a href="https://discord.gg/pGwRbMRjuH" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discord</a> (and the <a href="https://qr61.cn/oioUKl/qtksKk2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Shanghai testbed WeChat group</a> for participants in China).</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">What experience level is required?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>All levels are welcome — we provide baseline examples and tutorials.</p></div></div>
          </section>

          <section class="faq-card" id="faq-g2">
            <div class="faq-card-h"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"/><path d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"/><path d="M4 22h16"/><path d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22"/><path d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22"/><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"/></svg><h2>The competition</h2><span class="faq-card-c">6 questions</span></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">What are the tasks?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Three independent tracks — Task 1: Cable Routing &amp; Plugging; Task 2: Deformable Material Handling (Thermal Pad Placement); Task 3: Assisted Living &amp; Feeding. Enter one or more; each is ranked independently.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">Which simulators are used?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>NVIDIA Isaac Sim and MuJoCo. The MuJoCo version of Task 2 is not in the release (deformable-object fidelity isn't ready yet); if you build your own, it still counts.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">What teleoperation interfaces are provided?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p><a href="https://franka.de/de/gello" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Franka Duo GELLO</a>, Keyboard Control, Foot Pedal Control, and VR Control.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">Do I need to travel?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Primarily simulation-based — the open benchmark needs no travel. Teams advancing to real-world validation get a hands-on bench-testing window (Aug 10 – Aug 19, 2026), then an organizer-run testing window (Aug 20 – Aug 31, 2026) where you keep submitting code and the organizers run the robots.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">When are the simulation packages and baselines released?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>The first public release — simulation environments, the Teleoperation Toolkit, benchmark documentation, and baseline examples — is imminent. Watch <a href="https://discord.gg/pGwRbMRjuH" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discord</a> and the website for the release announcement.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">How will submissions be evaluated?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>The official rulebook and evaluation metrics are released together with the benchmark package; submission instructions follow.</p></div></div>
          </section>

          <section class="faq-card" id="faq-g3">
            <div class="faq-card-h"><svg class="faq-ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="16" height="16" x="4" y="4" rx="2"/><rect width="6" height="6" x="9" y="9" rx="1"/><path d="M9 2v2"/><path d="M15 2v2"/><path d="M9 20v2"/><path d="M15 20v2"/><path d="M2 9h2"/><path d="M2 15h2"/><path d="M20 9h2"/><path d="M20 15h2"/></svg><h2>Compute</h2><span class="faq-card-c">2 questions</span></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">What compute can I get, and how do I apply?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Three grant programs, open now on the <a href="compute-apply.html">compute grants page</a> — Google Cloud (up to US$1,000 of A100), Computational Freedom (RTX 4090 / L40S, mainland-China teams), and AMD Instinct MI300X (shared 8× MI300X in Taipei). Mainland teams should use Computational Freedom or MI300X.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-qa is-open"><button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="true"><span class="faq-q-t">Do I need my own GPU?</span><svg class="faq-chev" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></button><div class="faq-a"><p>Not necessarily — the grants above are intended to cover compute needs.</p></div></div>
